Feature: Validate login functionality of Orangle HRM application

  Scenario Outline: User should be able to login successfully with valid credentials.
    Given Browser launches and user is on the login page
    When User passes valid <username> and <password>
    And Clicks on login button
    Then User is now logged in and dashboard page is viewed
    And Finally logs out from application

    Examples: 
      | username |  | password |
      | Admin    |  | admin123 |
      | Admin    |  | admin124 |
      | Admin    |  | admin125 |
